#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/image.rst:283
msgid "Lightning LORA Support"
msgstr "Lightning LORA サポート"

#: ../../source/models/model_abilities/image.rst:285
msgid ""
"Lightning LORA performs distillation on models in the form of LoRA, reducing"
" the number of inference steps while maintaining model performance, and "
"significantly speeding up inference. The following models currently support "
"this LoRA:"
msgstr ""
"Lightning "
"LoRAは、モデルをLoRA形式で蒸留し、モデルの性能を維持しつつ推論ステップ数を削減し、推論速度を大幅に向上させます。現在、以下のモデルがこのLoRAをサポートしています："

